main event: An object fell from the sky in Chengtu, China.
interesting points: The object was silver in color and rectangular in shape.,It measured 10 inches in length, 5 inches in width, and 1 inch in thickness.,There was a piece of white paper on the bottom of the object.,Inside the object, there were four small batteries and two radio transmitter tubes.,The object had English inscriptions.
witness description: S. Elliott from the 5th Air Force Weather
